<!-- Products index page -->
<a id="products"></a>
<dt class="col-sm-1">Products</dt>

<dd class="col-sm-11">This page shows list of all active products present currently in database. Reference Code column is linked to product profile. Edit icon, <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-edit"></i> will take you directly to <Edit Product> form, where you can change all product attributes, except reference code. Optional "notes' field is only visible to you and can be used to store product-specific info. 
</dd>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<!-- Clients index page -->
<a id="clients"></a>
<dt class="col-sm-1">Clients</dt>

<dd class="col-sm-11">List of clients in database. Client name column (first) is linked to client profile. Edit icon, <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-edit"></i> will take you directly to <Edit Client> form, where you can change client attributes. Required attributes of Client form are: Name, Type, Price Type, Country and Email
</dd>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<!-- Orders index page -->
<a id="orders"></a>
<dt class="col-sm-1">Orders</dt>

<dd class="col-sm-11">This page shows list of orders, most recent first. Client name column (first) is linked to client profile. Last column contains status drop-down which allows you to change order status. 
Drop-down box at the top of the page allows you to filter orders by client. Grand total at the bottom shows total value of all orders in Euros using current USD/EUR FX conversion rate.
</dd>
